column4: 159340198611645e-05;tags2con delicious;"The tags2con dataset has been manually created by a group of human annotators that linked del.icio.us tags to their real meaning.

column1: A subset of a delicious dump has been used to create the tags2con dataset
column2: a set of 500 user-bookmarks pairs have been selected randomly and all the tags used by these pairs have been manually cleaned and disambiguated to WordNet synsets.

column1: More user-bookmark are being currently annotated.";http://disi.unitn.it/~knowdive/dataset/delicious/;-;0

column16: 0011208209818918528;TAXREF-LD: Linked Data French Taxonomic Register;"TAXREF-LD is the Linked Data representation of TAXREF (https://inpn.mnhn.fr/programme/referentiel-taxonomique-taxref?lg=en)
column17: the French national taxonomical register for fauna
column19: that covers mainland France and overseas territories.

column1: TAXREF-LD is a joint initiative of the National Museum of Natural History (http://www.mnhn.fr/) and the I3S laboratory (http://www.i3s.unice.fr/) (Université Côte d'Azur
column3: Inria). Its model is described in [1].

column1: [1] Michel F.
column3: Tercerie S. & Faron-Zucker C. (2017). A Model to Represent Nomenclatural and Taxonomic Information as Linked Data. Application to the French Taxonomic Register
column4: TAXREF. In _Proceedings of the 2nd International Workshop on Semantics for Biodiversity (S4BioDiv) co-located with ISWC 2017_ vol. 1933. Vienna

column16: 413955424741993e-05;URIBurner;"A service that delivers RDF-based structured descriptions of Web addressable resources in a variety of formats through Generic HTTP URIs.

column2: which takes an existing Web-accessible resource (webpage
column3: media) and generates an RDF graph of its metadata using existing well-known ontologies as well as site-specific knowledge. URIBurner then re-presents this data as either a new HTML webpage
column4: or directly as RDF in a variety of serializations (RDF/XML
